## G — Filter System Spec

**Filter dimensions (6 + search + sort):**
1. `type`: luxury-home | condo | penthouse | villa | estate (checkbox group)
2. `status`: for-sale | sold | leased (radio/pill)
3. `priceRange`: [min, max] slider — $500K to $25M (step $250K)
4. `beds`: 1+ | 2+ | 3+ | 4+ | 5+ (pill group)
5. `baths`: 1+ | 2+ | 3+ | 4+ (pill group — CEO guidance to restore)
6. `region`: All | Middle East | Europe | North America | Asia Pacific | South America (select/pill)
7. `search`: text input against title + city + country (debounced 200ms)
8. `sort`: Price High–Low | Price Low–High | Newest | Sqft Largest (select)

**Filter state shape (in App.jsx):**
```js
const [filters, setFilters] = useState({
  type: [],        // [] = all
  status: 'all',
  priceMin: 0,
  priceMax: 25000000,
  bedsMin: 0,
  bathsMin: 0,
  region: 'all',
  search: '',
  sort: 'price-desc',
});
```

